---

<Layout title="Rocksiders — Cheat sheet" description="Cheat sheet compact des classes utilitaires (Rocksiders / Rocks Theme).">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 grid gap-8 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[260px_minmax(0,1fr)]">
      <aside
        class="sticky top-0 z-20 self-start md:top-[calc(var(--space-10)-var(--space-1))] md:col-start-1 bg-[var(--surface-card)] border border-[var(--border-soft)] rounded-lg p-3 md:p-4 shadow-sm"
        data-docs-nav
      >
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)] mb-3" data-docs-nav-title>Navigation</p>
        <nav class="flex md:flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-auto pb-1" id="rocks-cheatsheet-nav">
          {sections.map((item) => (
            <a
              href={`#${item.id}`}
              data-target={item.id}
              class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--text-strong)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-muted)] transition-colors"
            >
              {item.label}
            </a>
          ))}
        </nav>
      </aside>

      <div class="space-y-14 md:col-start-2 min-w-0">
        <header class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-[var(--text-muted)]">Rocksiders DS</p>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text-strong)]">Cheat sheet — classes utilitaires</h1>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
            Liste compacte (copiable) des classes utilitaires détectées dans le CSS Rocksiders, organisée par thèmes.
          </p>
          <div class="doc-card">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Sommaire</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <a class="btn-primary is-outline" href="/wiki-rocks-utilitaires">Rocks — Utilitaires</a>
              <a class="btn-primary is-outline" href="/wiki-rocks-layout">Rocks — Layout</a>
              <a class="btn-primary" href="/wiki-rocks-cheatsheet">Rocks — Cheat sheet</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="badge-pill">Copiable</span>
            <span class="badge-pill">Référence</span>
            <span class="badge-pill">Rocksiders</span>
          </div>
        </header>

        <section id="intro" class="scroll-mt-24 space-y-4" data-spy-section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)]">Contexte</h2>
          <div class="note-callout">
            <p class="note-callout__title">Note</p>
            <p class="note-callout__text">
              Cette page n’implémente pas ces classes dans ce projet Astro : elle sert de documentation et de base de mapping.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="doc-card space-y-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">Astuce : colle ces listes dans un fichier TODO quand tu fais la migration / ré-implémentation.</p>
            <Code lang="text" code={`Source: Rocks Theme (rocksiders.com)\nDoc: CHEATSHEET-CLASSES.md`} />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="espacement" class="scroll-mt-24 space-y-4" data-spy-section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)]">Espacement</h2>
          <div class="doc-card space-y-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">Padding / margin / helpers + variantes (suffixes l/m/xl).</p>
            <Code lang="text" code={formatList(spacing)} />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="typo" class="scroll-mt-24 space-y-4" data-spy-section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)]">Texte / Typo</h2>
          <div class="doc-card space-y-3">
            <Code lang="text" code={formatList(typo)} />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="couleurs" class="scroll-mt-24 space-y-4" data-spy-section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)]">Couleurs</h2>
          <div class="doc-card space-y-3">
            <Code lang="text" code={formatList(colors)} />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="layout" class="scroll-mt-24 space-y-4" data-spy-section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)]">Layout / Display</h2>
          <div class="doc-card space-y-3">
            <Code lang="text" code={formatList(layout)} />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="effets" class="scroll-mt-24 space-y-4" data-spy-section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)]">Bordures / Effets</h2>
